      "text": "Hide was a student at a Fire Nation school who often bullied the other pupils. He fancied himself to be On Ji's boyfriend and was highly possessive of her, though she did not show any affection toward him in return."
    },
    {
      "body": "Hide regularly tried to draw fights with other students, and would easily weasel his way out of trouble. He was a star example of what the ${link_0} school system could produce: a muscular build and a weak mind. He was destined to grow up to become a strict ${link_1} officer who would be hated by his subordinates.",
