      "text": "Hide regularly tried to draw fights with other students, and would easily weasel his way out of trouble. He was a star example of what the Fire Nation school system could produce: a muscular build and a weak mind. He was destined to grow up to become a strict Fire Nation military officer who would be hated by his subordinates."
    },
    {
      "body": "When ${link_0}, who had adopted the alias Kuzon after his ${link_1}, came to the Fire Nation school, everyone assumed he was a new student from the ${link_2}. After dismissal, Aang met On Ji, who was friendly to him. Hide, seeing \"Kuzon\" and On Ji together, made sure Aang knew that she was his girlfriend by starting a brief confrontation.",
