      ],
      "text": "When Aang, who had adopted the alias Kuzon after his old friend, came to the Fire Nation school, everyone assumed he was a new student from the Fire Nation colonies. After dismissal, Aang met On Ji, who was friendly to him. Hide, seeing \"Kuzon\" and On Ji together, made sure Aang knew that she was his girlfriend by starting a brief confrontation."
    },
    {
      "body": "During a band class, Aang got in trouble for dancing, which was not allowed. On Ji, however, was amused by the dance, and Aang offered to show it to her during recess. Hide ${link_0} at Aang as he heard this remark and exclaimed that \"nobody [showed his] On Ji anything, especially movements\". He subsequently attempted to hit Aang; however, the latter skillfully evaded every attempted blow, eventually causing Hide to lose his balance and fall over, without utilizing any ${link_1} or even touching him - which got Aang into trouble for \"beating up\" another student.",
